name: donfig
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "donfig" %}
{% set version = "0.7.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7e3993981b7312edb16098989e4cb084ff58c1b1d8e9878c7c0107eabf18dbfa

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python
  script: '{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv '

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.7
    - pip
    - setuptools
    - pyyaml
  run:
    - python >=3.7
    - pyyaml

test:
  imports:
    - donfig
    - donfig.tests
  requires:
    - pytest

about:
  home: https://github.com/pytroll/donfig
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Python package for configuring a python package
  doc_url: https://donfig.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/pytroll/donfig

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - djhoese
    - mraspaud
    - pnuu
    - adybbroe
    - mrocklin
    - jcrist
    - jhamman
